metadata.name: Call To Meme
metadata.description:
Inspired from Liberty Loans poster from circa 1917-1918, this is a  
Call to memers and collectoors to contribute and seize the MEMEs in whichever way possible. We must defend our MEMEs with our own keys and HW wallets, stop relying on Centralised authorities.

United we can ward off, all the evil in the space and make a better and safer space together
